<passage>

   <title>Mike's mother and father</title>

   <paragraph>Mike, Mike,</paragraph>

   <paragraph>What's your mother like?</paragraph>

   <paragraph>She's kind and she's quiet.</paragraph>

   <paragraph>Her hair is short and her dress is red.</paragraph>

   <paragraph>Mike, Mike,</paragraph>

   <paragraph>What's your father like?</paragraph>

   <paragraph>He's tall and he's strong.</paragraph>

   <paragraph>His hair is short and his legs are long.</paragraph>

</passage>